  <acronym>PIANO</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open Label Single Arm Study to Investigate the Safety and Efficacy of Multiple Administrations of NI-0801, a Fully Human Anti-CXCL10 Monoclonal Antibody in PBC Patients With an Incomplete Response to Ursodeoxycholic Acid</official_title>
