  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess safety and efficacy of multiple doses of NI-0801 in
      primary biliary cirrhosis patients with an inadequate response to ursodeoxycholic acid.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
